features: 【360° Omnidirectional Protection with 4 Cameras】The Neideso dash camera N300 does not obstruct your field of view and allows you to record both front and right at the same time with 4 cameras. The angle of the camera can be adjusted not only forward, but also backward and car directions. You can set it at the angle you want to shoot without being caught by traffic conflicts but also from potential responsibilities.

【Adopts a design that does not interfere with your field of view】With a size of 2.2 x 7.1 x 2.0 inches (5.5 x 18 x 5 cm), this 4 camera 150° wide angle lens allows you to record road without any blind spots. CPL filters sold separately to reduce reflections, increase contrast and increase color saturation while maintaining color reproduction.

【Event Recording】There is a method of recording "Always Recording" that is constantly recorded and "event recording" when the engine switch is turned on and turned off in the event of a certain impact or airbag operation during constant recording.

【24 Hours Parking Mode】: Radar Intelligent Monitoring System,In the car off state, the front 3 ~ 4 meters range to monitor the object close to the car, 5 seconds quick start machine,the car dashcam automatically record video 1 minute, and a minute later will automatically stop recording; recording 1 minute after if the object continues to detect the movement has been recording until the object left, the machine will automatically stop recording and shut down.

【GPS Function & Smartphone App Supported】 It can acquire car location information with GPS, record the route and speed of the car, and connect with video and map. Also important as evidence in the event of an accident. The recorded video can also be seen on the smartphone app, and the method of the time and running route are displayed on the map of the smartphone app.

【Super Night Vision Function】 Equipped with 8 LED infrared and WDR (wide dynamic range) to prevent overexposure caused by headlights, and to record license plates. It detects sudden changes in brightness, and automatically adjusts brightness for clear recording.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Good value camera needs better software
reviews.reviewText: Good product for the price. They ought to invest a little more in customer service or product support because there is no telephone number or email on file. I would like to see this technology improved. I am unaware if there is a product that is closer to meeting my needs. What would it take to save all of these videos on the cloud? The SD card can be stolen and that makes the data vulnerable for loss. I also installed the 24 hour parking radar and it seems to work fine however the problem is with the app integration since I can only view the videos once I start my car. I thought I could connect the dash cam to a hotspot and have the videos accessible on my phone via the app from far away at any time just like a blink or ring camera. Aside from that as far as driving is concerned this dash cam will do just fine recording while on the road. In the event of an accident and I must save the evidence (hopefully this doesn’t happen) I guess I will have to screen record my videos or take out the SD card since I don’t think it’s possible to download the videos and save it to my phone or cloud. I reported a bug on the TsCam app because the menu options contained words spelled incorrectly words like Videos and Emergency are spelled like “Vidoes” and “ Emgncery” so please fix.
